de.intarsys.pdf.app.action
Class TriggerEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      de.intarsys.pdf.app.action.TriggerEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TriggerEvent
extends EventObject

An event that leads to the processing of an action or action sequence.

The source of the event is always the COSObject responsible for the event, for example the document for document level events, the field for field events and so on.
